para_trans: Regarding the sanction of new Primary Health Centres at Mauje, Ansarwada, Shedol, Kappiga, Dawanhiparga and Hippalgaon (total 5) in Nilanga constituency of Latur district.
Government Decision No: Establishment-2024 / P.No.226 / Health-4
Read: - Letter No. of Joint Director, Health Services, (Pre-Centre / Sub-Centre / Dispensaries), Mumbai: J. No.
Asa / Room 7A / T-5 / Banpetwadi / Prakendra / Manzoor / Satara / 2872-74, dated 29.07.2024.
Preamble: - Mouje, Ansarwada, Ta., Nilanga constituency in Latur district. Nilanga, Shedol, Ta. Nilanga,
Nearby, Ta. Devani, Dawanhipparga, Ta. Devani and Hippalgaon, Ta. 5 at Shirur Anantpal, G. Latur
New Primary Health Centre sanctioned to provide health facilities to the citizens of the area
The matter of sanctioning a primary health centre at the site is under the consideration of the government as it is necessary to do so.
The following decisions are being taken in this regard.
Mauje, Ansarwada, Ta., Nilanga constituency in Latur district. Nilanga, Shedol, Ta. Nilanga,
Nearby, Ta. Devani, Dawanhipparga, Ta. Devani and Hippalgaon, Ta. 5 at Shirur Anantpal, G. Latur
Approval is being given to sanction a new primary health centre as a "special case."
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
